SELECT [t].[malaptop], [t].[cpu], [t].[giaban], [t].[gpu], [t].[hardware], [t].[hinh], [t].[mahang], [t].[manhinh], [t].[manhucau], [t].[mota], [t].[ngaycapnhat], [t].[pin], [t].[ram], [t].[soluongton], [t].[tenlaptop], [t].[trangthai], [d].[madanhgia], [d].[malaptop], [d].[ngaydanhgia], [d].[noidung], [d].[ten], [d].[trangthai], [d].[vote]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [l].[malaptop], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [Laptop] AS [l]
    WHERE [l].[malaptop] = @__malaptop_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [DanhGia] AS [d] ON [t].[malaptop] = [d].[malaptop]
ORDER BY [t].[malaptop]

CREATE TABLE [Replies] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Ten] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Noidung] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [l].[malaptop], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [l].[malaptop], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

    SELECT TOP(1) [l].[malaptop], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [Laptop] AS [l]
    WHERE [l].[malaptop] = @__malaptop_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [DanhGia] AS [d] ON [t].[malaptop] = [d].[malaptop]
ORDER BY [t].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [l].[malaptop], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [DanhGia] AS [d] ON [t].[malaptop] = [d].[malaptop]
ORDER BY [t].[malaptop]

    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Laptop] AS [l]
        WHERE [l].[malaptop] = @__malaptop_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
